 git init to start new git repository ****************

 git add . to add all files in current directory*******

 git commit -m "message" to commit all files in current directory********

 git push -u origin main to push all files in current directory to github********

 git status to check status of all files in current directory****************   

 git rm -r --cached node_modules to remove all files in current directory******** which are not in use in github**********************

 